    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyUI
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 963142763}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: enemiesLeftText
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1757584678}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyController
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 963142761}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: '"I see something up ahead!" Brad pointed out.\n\n[Press X key to continue]'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I forgot Brad can talk. It is so different when you look at an inanimate
        object versus a living creature.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: '"Hey hey hey!! It''s another weapon! The <u>Ice Hammer</u>, I think
        I recognize her! Please please please, pick her up!" Brad begged.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: So there are more... this is truly disgusting. Looks like I'll be finding
        more of them as I make my way through.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: '"L-L-Look, Fern. She''s kinda my ex, but like, I am still madly in
        love with her! So please, let me have another chance to make it up to her!"'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: '"She''s kinda <b><u>freezes people up</b></u> when <b><u>they first
        talk to her</b></u>, but they feel fine again after <b><u>a second</b></u>
        or so!!"'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4788537577470390567, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: ExitDoor (1)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
