  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Exit
  openDoor: {fileID: 0}
  enemiesHolder: {fileID: 0}
  storyUI: {fileID: 963142763}
  storyLines:
  - '"I see something up ahead!" - Brad.'
  - I forgot Brad can talk. It is so different when you look at an inanimate object
    versus a living creature.
  - '"Hey hey hey!! It''s another weapon! I think I recognize her! Please please
    please, pick her up!" - Brad.'
  - So there are more... this is truly disgusting. Looks like I'll be finding more
    of them as I make my way through.
  - '"L-l-look, Fern. She''s kinda my ex, but like, I am still madly in love with
    her! So please, let me have another chance to make it up to her!" - Brad.'
  - '"She''s kinda <b>cold</b> when <b>anyone first meets her</b>, but you feel fine
    again after <b>two seconds</b> or so!!" - Brad.'
  storyController: {fileID: 963142761}
  enemiesLeftText: {fileID: 0}
